lead_paragraph: The Olympic Council of Asia (OCA) has decided to set up five new sub offices to enable it to function effectively while the row with the Kuwait government continues over its headquarters in the Gulf State.

headline.print_headline: Asia Council Sets Up Sub Offices as Kuwait Row Rumbles
